                     <interp inst="t18290219-93-person917" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I settled with him on the Saturday morning, and he had a suit of clothes of me for the money I owed him - not one farthing do I owe him.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 31.</p>
